pos_mean_info_list.mean: 有深刻见解的，富有洞察力的

word_group.brief_definition: 深刻的洞察力；深刻视界；真知灼见
展示出洞察力；显示出洞察力

bilingual.target: 他的敏锐洞察力令人印象深刻。

bilingual.source: His words were full of wisdom and insight.
bilingual.target: 他的词语充满了智慧和洞察力。

bilingual.source: She has a remarkable insight into human behavior.
bilingual.target: 她对人类行为有着非凡的洞察力。

bilingual.source: The prophet was known for his wisdom and insight.
bilingual.target: 先知以他的智慧和洞察力而闻名。

bilingual.source: Her insight helped solve the complex problem.
bilingual.target: 她的洞察力帮助解决了这个复杂的问题。

bilingual.source: Her insight allows her to understand others' feelings.
bilingual.target: 她的洞察力使她能够理解他人的感受。

bilingual.source: This book provides deep insight into human behavior.
bilingual.target: 这本书提供了对人类行为的深刻洞察力。

bilingual.source: Her insight helped her solve many complex problems.
bilingual.target: 她的洞察力帮助她解决了很多复杂的问题。

bilingual.source: Through observation, he gained new insight into the issue.
bilingual.target: 通过观察，他获得了对问题的新的洞察力。

bilingual.source: The seminar offered valuable insight into the latest research.
bilingual.target: 研讨会提供了对最新研究的宝贵洞察力。

list.abstract: 澳大利亚休闲时装品牌，Insight是一个充满古怪念头有些疯癫的品牌，诞生于悉尼的北海滩边，那里充满了活力四射的冲浪场面。忠实于它的冲浪传统，它创造了融合音乐、艺术和滑板文化的都市冲浪时尚，炫目耀眼，蓬勃优雅。它不饰雕琢的时尚、配饰甚至滑板十分形象化地刻画上了真实冲浪场面以及街道上的滑板表演。

yingyinNormal.en: The S.T.R.I.K.E and Insight crew are Hydra as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 特战队和洞察计划团队也是。

yingyinNormal.en: There is some insight into what Cathy brought up. Backpedaling as weakness.
yingyinNormal.zh: Cathy 提出的观点不无道理。变卦就是软弱。

yingyinNormal.en: We're worried they're thinking of leaving with them. Do you have any insight? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们担心客户正考虑着和他们一块离开，你有什么想法吗? 没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Nick Fury used your friendship to coerce this council into delaying Project Insight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尼克弗瑞利用你们的友谊迫使理事会推迟洞察计划。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm here to ask a favor. I want you to call for a vote. Project Insight has to be delayed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来找你帮个忙，我想请你发动一次投票，洞察计划必须得推迟。

yingyinNormal.en: We've already had it, Mr. Secretary. This council moves to immediately reactivate Project Insight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们已经讨论过了，部长先生，理事会已经作出决定立即重启洞察计划。

yingyinNormal.en: And through understanding each other's popular cultures, we gain insight into each other's hearts and true selves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通过理解对方的流行文化，我们看到了对方的内心和真实的自我。

yingyinNormal.en: Once the Helicarriers reach three thousand feet, they'll triangulate with Insight Satellites becoming fully weaponized.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当天空母舰飞到3000英尺高，他们会和洞察卫星组成三角形，然后彻底武器化。

yingyinNormal.en: That was Arnold's key insight, the thing that led the hosts to their awakening, suffering. The pain that the world is not as you want it to be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是阿诺德的关键见解，是可以导致接待员们觉醒的东西，苦难折磨，察觉到世界并非如你希望那般后的痛苦。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir, I briefed the First Lady on the Milkin operation. I thought she might have some insight, given her experience working directly with Russia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生，我已向第一夫人说明了米尔金行动。考虑到她曾与俄国有过直接交涉，我想也许她会有一些见解。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to share with you the biggest insight in the language learning that was discovered almost 50 years ago by doctor Paul Pimsleur, someone you could call the Einstein of learning language.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要和大家分享一个50年前发现的关于语言学习的重要观察，这是由Paul Pimsleur博士发现的，他堪称是语言学习方面的爱因斯坦。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an understanding of what something is like

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>insight</highlight> that curiosity can drive you to do self-destructive things is a profound one.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 好奇心可以驱使你做一些自我毁灭的事情，这是一个深刻的见解。

sense_info_list.en: the capacity to gain an accurate and deep intuitive understanding of a person or thing

examination_example.sentence: Many first-generation students lack <highlight>insight</highlight> about why they are struggling.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多第一代学生对自己为什么要如此奋斗缺乏洞察力。

affix_sense_info.affix_sense_chinese: 否定前缀, 表示"不, 无"

word_usage.usage: insight作名词，表示“了解；洞悉”时，常与into sth.搭配使用，如：insights into life

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 富有洞察力的；有深刻见解的

word_family.mean: n. 洞察力；洞悉力；自知力；深刻见解；顿悟

sense_info_list.en: a deep understanding of a person or thing

examination_example.sentence: This <highlight>insight</highlight> not only explains why we might hold our tongue at a dinner party or look the other way.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一观点不仅解释了为什么我们会在晚宴上保持沉默或朝其他方向看。

examination_example.sentence: The point to win the diseases of childhood were eliminated, but this did not provide any <highlight>insight</highlight> into childhood development.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 战胜儿童疾病的意义被消除了，但这并没有提供任何关于儿童发展的见解。

examination_example.sentence: Smartphones might transform the way we live and work: by offering <highlight>insights</highlight> into human psychology and behavior and, thus, supporting smarter social science.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是智能手机可能改变我们生活和工作方式：通过提供对人类心理和行为的见解，从而支持更智能的社会科学的方式。

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 富有洞察力的；有深刻见解的

word_family.mean: n. 洞察力；洞悉力；自知力；深刻见解；顿悟

sense_info_list.en: a deep understanding of a person or thing

examination_example.sentence: Cultures without numbers also offer <highlight>insight</highlight> into the cognitive influence of particular numeric traditions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有数字的文化也提供了对特定数字传统认知影响的洞察。

examination_example.sentence: Our studies have yielded one main <highlight>insight</highlight>: Students' beliefs about change are related to their ability to cope, succeed academically and maintain good mental health.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们的研究得出了一个主要观点：学生对变化的信念与他们的应对能力、学业成功和保持良好心理健康有关。

examination_example.sentence: We gain <highlight>insight</highlight> in cognition changes, and may possibly discover ways to slow the rate of decline.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们深入了解了认知能力的变化，并可能发现减缓衰退速度的方法。

sense_info_list.en: the capacity to gain an accurate and deep intuitive understanding of a person or thing

examination_example.sentence: The realizations I had in that process helped me gain <highlight>insights</highlight> and ultimately got me ready to integrate self-care into my daily life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我在这个过程中的认识帮助我获得了洞察力，并最终让我准备好将自我护理融入我的日常生活。

examination_example.sentence: She is a mayor of <highlight>insight</highlight> and vision.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她是一位有洞察力和远见的市长。
